description: The Inscribables collection is a special collection of 1700 inscriptions minted on the Bitcoin network on Pizza and block 78 sats. These inscriptions were created to reward holders of core projects within the Ordinal ecosystem and to onboard individuals to the Inscribable platform upon its launch. This is your chance to become a part of a groundbreaking initiative in the world of inscriptions!
name: The Inscribables(Scribe Squad)
